macros.usage_example:
Schema::create('plans', function (Blueprint $t) {
    $t->string('id', 64)->primary();
    $t->workspaceable();
    $t->string('name_slug');
    $t->translations();          // ← adds the `translations` JSONB column
    $t->timestamps();
});

macros.read_shape:
Trait accessors return the value for the active locale. Direct DB shape (never exposed on the wire by default): {
  "en": {"name": "Team", "description": "For growing organisations"},
  "fr": {"name": "Équipe", "description": "Pour les organisations en croissance"},
  "ar": {"name": "الفريق", "description": "..."}
}
